settings.bury_freebeat_title: Why Invest in a Tuscany Yellow Spin Bike From freebeat™?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: When you invest in a freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow spin bike, you don’t need to decide between style and substance. Sure, it’s got style: between the bright yellow color and cute compact design, it looks more like a statement piece than workout equipment. But aesthetics are only a fraction of the bike’s beauty. This is a spin bike that delivers. It’s fully immersive and interactive, with thousands of gamified classes and exercise experiences. The freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow Boom Bike is also part of our Boom Bike line, which features an authentic, heart-pumping cycling experience with an affordable price tag.

settings.bury_freebeat_title: How Does freebeat™ Deliver an Authentic Cycling Experience at Home?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: The freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow exercise bike puts you right in the action. Become immersed in your workout through smart technology that tracks and matches your performance, artist-generated visuals, pumping tunes, and dynamic lightstrips that match your tempo. You can even meet a countrywide squad of users to play against.

settings.bury_freebeat_title: What Can I Expect From the freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow Cycling Bike?
settings.bury_freebeat_info1: The freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow cycling bike is one of our Boom home cardio machines and offers the following:
settings.bury_freebeat_info2: Dynamic Lightstrips: Let’s party. The freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow exercise bike features lightstrips that use smart technology to match your pace and light up your room to the tempo of your workout. Gamified Workouts: The freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow exercise bike provides the ultimate workout experience for gamers — it makes you the main character. Our unique gamified cycling system features artist-generated backgrounds, an unreal soundtrack, and thousands of gamified classes and exercise experiences to create a fully immersive workout. You can even challenge other users to some friendly competition.
settings.bury_freebeat_info3: 15.6” Interactive HD Touch Screen: Every freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow cycling bike features a 180-degree rotating HD touch screen, allowing you to seamlessly swivel between classes and fully immerse yourself into the world of your workout. Auto-Resistance System: Your freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow indoor bike works with you, not the other day around. Your bike uses smart technology to evaluate and adjust your resistance level to match your pace and abilities. Plus, if you ever want to choose your resistance settings, you can do so manually. Smart Saddle Detection+: Your freebeat™ Tuscany Yellow exercise bike isn’t just stylish and effective — it’s safe. Every freebeat™ bike saddle has built-in smart sensors that detect when you get on and off the bike.
